1
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:13,000
"Double Helix"

2
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:16,120
After the New Year,

3
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:18,560
if I still insist on being with you,

4
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:21,080
I'll no longer be a part of the Lu family.

5
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:27,959
Do you understand what that means?

6
00:01:29,519 --> 00:01:30,519
It's even harder for me

7
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,319
to make a choice than it is for him.

8
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:36,760
What do you want me to do?

9
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:39,599
I...

10
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,439
I don't know.

11
00:01:47,959 --> 00:01:48,959
Xiao Chen.

12
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,760
I'm not going to leave you.

13
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,239
It's just that for a while,

14
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,040
I won't be able to give you a good life.

15
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,799
I can't give you a big villa.

16
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,800
I can't buy you a luxury car.

17
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,560
I...

18
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,879
I think this small apartment is just fine.

19
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:17,120
Well...

20
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,119
there won't be a driver,

21
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,080
an assistant,

22
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,240
or a housekeeper.

23
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:23,199
You'll have to do everything yourself.

24
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,759
That's how I've lived for
the past 20-something years.

25
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:28,039
You don't believe me？.

26
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,880
It's not that I don't believe you.

27
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:31,840
It's just...

28
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:34,240
this isn't the life I want to give you.

29
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:36,799
I only want to give you the best.

30
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,560
Lu Feng.

31
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,400
I don't need all that.

32
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,120
All I want...

33
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,680
is to be with you.

34
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,960
But...

35
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:57,359
what if I can't give you the
things you like and want?

36
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,320
What if I can't provide
any of that for you?

37
00:03:01,319 --> 00:03:02,319
What then?

38
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,080
I have a job too.

39
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,038
The things I like,

40
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:10,000
I can buy for myself.

41
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,360
I can even...

42
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:14,759
support you.

43
00:03:16,319 --> 00:03:18,000
Who needs you to support them?

44
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,159
So...

45
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:28,879
you're choosing...

46
00:03:30,639 --> 00:03:31,719
not to break up with me.

47
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:33,759
Is that right?

48
00:03:39,159 --> 00:03:40,400
Do you want to break up?

49
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,439
Then we won't.

50
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:48,599
We'll...

51
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:51,719
always be together.

52
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,800
I,

53
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,560
Lu Feng,

54
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,840
will never leave Cheng
Yichen in this lifetime.

55
00:04:05,759 --> 00:04:06,759
You'll...

56
00:04:08,439 --> 00:04:09,960
never leave me.

57
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,400
Right?

58
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:43,279
But...

59
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,120
for the New Year...

60
00:04:46,319 --> 00:04:47,720
shouldn't you...

61
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,439
still go back to the US?

62
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:51,759
Even if you give up the inheritance,

63
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,720
your family...

64
00:04:53,759 --> 00:04:56,399
they're probably hoping
to reunite with you.

65
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,000
You are my family.

66
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:12,959
For the New Year,

67
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:16,680
I just want to be by your side.

68
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:17,959
Can I...

69
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:20,439
go home with you?

70
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:21,879
My mom, she...

71
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,000
I won't go to your house.

72
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,560
I'll just book a hotel nearby.

73
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,720
Okay?

74
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:03,400
(Episode 7: My family and my lover
are both of my weaknesses)

75
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,199
Qin Lang.
Auntie.

76
00:06:06,839 --> 00:06:08,438
I told you to go rest.

77
00:06:08,439 --> 00:06:10,439
We can't have a guest doing all the work.

78
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,319
Auntie,

79
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,040
please don't be so formal with me.

80
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:14,920
My parents are abroad all year.

81
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,000
For the New Year...

82
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:17,199
if you hadn't taken me in,

83
00:06:17,224 --> 00:06:18,504
who knows where I'd be wandering right now.

84
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,680
Yeah, Mom.

85
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:22,240
He only knows how to
roll the dough, not wrap it.

86
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,480
Just let him do that.

87
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:26,199
Yi-chen, is that any
way to talk to your boss?

88
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,520
Don't say "taken me in,"
that sounds so distant.

89
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,959
You let our Yi-chen

90
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:33,359
work at your place

91
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,639
to earn his tuition.

92
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:36,758
I can't thank you enough.

93
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:37,999
It's nothing, Auntie.

94
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,800
Yi-chen is

95
00:06:38,801 --> 00:06:39,878
good-looking,

96
00:06:39,879 --> 00:06:40,959
has a cheerful personality,

97
00:06:41,279 --> 00:06:43,079
and most importantly, he's a great singer.

98
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,399
With him at our...

99
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:49,016
With him as the resident
singer for our band,

100
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,959
our band's tickets
are almost always sold out.

101
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,920
Really?

102
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:54,639
A kid like him doesn't
have that kind of talent.

103
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,680
It's just because you think highly of him.

104
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:58,399
It's because you raised him well.

105
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,560
Really?

106
00:07:00,439 --> 00:07:02,000
Oh, not at all.

107
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,160
Bro, sit.

108
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:09,959
Let me make some room for you.

109
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:12,919
Look, the ones you wrapped are all leaking.

110
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,136
How are we supposed to eat these?

111
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,040
What are you laughing at?
Okay, okay.

112
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:15,839
I'll stop laughing.
Still laughing.

113
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,696
I'm not laughing, I'm not laughing.

114
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,720
Yi-chen.

115
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:20,639
Where are your manners?

116
00:08:11,959 --> 00:08:13,319
I forgot something important.

117
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:14,639
Xiao Chen,

118
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:16,336
go get a coin from the drawer in my room.

119
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,600
Scald it with boiling water.

120
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,959
Why do we need a coin?

121
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,216
We put it in the dumpling filling.

122
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,879
Whoever eats it will get rich.

123
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,560
Then can you just give it to me directly?

124
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:24,720
I'll give it to you.
Money-grubber.

125
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:26,439
Get back to work.

126
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,799
Bro, there's only one left.

127
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:40,799
Come on.

128
00:08:40,879 --> 00:08:41,879
Coming.

129
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,200
Mom,

130
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,840
what's that medicine on your nightstand?

131
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:57,039
Just some vitamins.

132
00:08:57,519 --> 00:08:58,679
Didn't I tell you

133
00:08:58,919 --> 00:09:00,775
not to trust those door-to-door
supplement salespeople?

134
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:02,399
A lot of those are unregulated products.

135
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,839
If you're not feeling well,

136
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,559
you have to tell me

137
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:05,919
or go to the hospital, okay?

138
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,200
Mom,

139
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:08,720
what's wrong?

140
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:13,039
Look at you all, so worried.

141
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,360
Mom's really fine.

142
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,279
It's just your aunt.

143
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,440
She said these are good for calcium.

144
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,279
She's been taking them for years.

145
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,559
Mom's really fine.

146
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:22,879
Really?

147
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:24,599
You're really not feeling unwell anywhere?

148
00:09:24,759 --> 00:09:25,759
No.

149
00:09:25,879 --> 00:09:27,239
You all stop worrying for nothing.

150
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:29,176
You have to tell us if
you're not feeling well.

151
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,519
I know, I know.

152
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:31,279
Yi-chen,

153
00:09:31,280 --> 00:09:32,720
go check if the water is boiling.

154
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,399
I'll go, I'll go.

155
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,320
Yichen, give me the coin. Here.

156
00:09:46,814 --> 00:09:49,560
[The kind of selfies people
in love send, from Lu Feng]

157
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:40,039
Everyone finished?

158
00:10:40,559 --> 00:10:41,080
I'll clean up.

159
00:10:41,081 --> 00:10:42,241
Mom, you go rest. I'll do it.

160
00:10:42,639 --> 00:10:44,080
Yeah, Mom, let my brother do it.

161
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:45,759
He only wrapped a few dumplings
and did nothing else.

162
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:47,679
We'll play cards with you.

163
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,000
Yeah, Auntie.

164
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,735
I've never played your local card games.

165
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:52,759
Please teach me.

166
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,320
I'm so relaxed.

167
00:10:54,639 --> 00:10:55,639
Let's go.

168
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,720
Wash them all properly!

169
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,559
Lu Feng.

170
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,000
Xiao Chen.

171
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:45,799
Lu Feng.
What are you doing here?

172
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:01,119
I was afraid I'd miss midnight

173
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:03,255
and wouldn't be able to
ring in the New Year with you.

174
00:12:03,279 --> 00:12:04,519
It's another year, Lu Feng.

175
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:06,039
Another year.

176
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:09,160
You have to stay with me all this year.

177
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:11,159
And next year too.

178
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,600
And the year after that.

179
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,440
And the year after that.

180
00:12:18,679 --> 00:12:19,679
Xiao Chen.

181
00:12:20,399 --> 00:12:21,960
Happy New Year.

182
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,679
Happy New Year.

183
00:12:58,559 --> 00:12:59,440
What are you smiling at?

184
00:12:59,441 --> 00:13:02,039
Smiling at you sneaking in
here in the middle of the night.

185
00:13:02,559 --> 00:13:05,039
If you keep talking like that,
I'm going to my brother's room.

186
00:13:06,159 --> 00:13:07,159
Sit.

187
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,240
Don't go.

188
00:13:21,159 --> 00:13:22,240
It's almost midnight.

189
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,800
This is our first time
spending New Year's together.

190
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,200
Stay and be with me.

191
00:13:30,399 --> 00:13:31,480
That's more like it.

192
00:13:36,559 --> 00:13:37,679
Happy New Year.

193
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:39,679
Yi-chen.

194
00:13:41,039 --> 00:13:42,759
Make a New Year's wish.

195
00:14:00,919 --> 00:14:01,919
Qin Lang.

196
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,878
When you told me once again,

197
00:14:04,879 --> 00:14:06,039
that you loved me,

198
00:14:07,039 --> 00:14:08,720
my wish had already come true.

199
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:12,559
Thank you for wishing me a Happy New Year.

200
00:14:24,639 --> 00:14:25,639
Qin Lang.

201
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:26,840
You did that on purpose.

202
00:14:45,399 --> 00:14:47,639
Yi-chen, get some rest.

203
00:15:04,953 --> 00:15:05,953
She's gone?

204
00:15:06,519 --> 00:15:07,519
She's gone.

205
00:16:50,759 --> 00:16:52,279
Where were you so early this morning?

206
00:16:52,559 --> 00:16:54,240
Why didn't you do the dishes yesterday?

207
00:16:54,799 --> 00:16:56,799
I went to buy breakfast, Mom.

208
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,456
Who's selling breakfast
during the New Year?

209
00:16:58,480 --> 00:16:59,639
So where's the breakfast?

210
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:02,519
Since it's the New Year, nothing was open.

211
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:04,360
We have breakfast at home.

212
00:17:04,759 --> 00:17:05,759
You're such a bad liar.

213
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:12,640
Come on, eat.

214
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,119
Oh, right.

215
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:21,518
In a couple of days, come with me
to visit your aunt for the New Year.

216
00:17:21,519 --> 00:17:23,119
She's found someone to introduce you to.

217
00:17:24,559 --> 00:17:25,559
A date?

218
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,480
I asked her to keep an eye out for you.

219
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,838
You're not getting any younger.

220
00:17:28,839 --> 00:17:30,399
It's time to think about settling down.

221
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:32,319
But I don't want to get married right now.

222
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:35,279
No one's saying you
have to get married now.

223
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,839
Just meet them first.

224
00:17:37,799 --> 00:17:40,440
Mom, I want to focus
on my career right now.

225
00:17:41,319 --> 00:17:42,920
You can do both at the same time.

226
00:17:43,079 --> 00:17:44,079
I...

227
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:47,440
Coming!

228
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:49,799
Hello, ma'am.
Happy New Year.

229
00:17:50,619 --> 00:17:51,780
Happy New Year.

230
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:53,599
And you are...?

231
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:54,920
I'm Zhuo Lan.

232
00:17:55,079 --> 00:17:56,720
I was Yi-chen's classmate in college.

233
00:17:59,359 --> 00:18:00,640
Please, come in. Come in.

234
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:01,720
Come on.

235
00:18:01,799 --> 00:18:02,880
Thank you, ma'am.

236
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,440
Have a seat, have a seat.

237
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:09,599
Yi-chen, go talk to your friend.

238
00:18:10,119 --> 00:18:10,799
Sit down.

239
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,160
I'll go get you some fruit.

240
00:18:12,599 --> 00:18:13,079
Okay.
Sit.

241
00:18:18,039 --> 00:18:19,079
You sit down, too.

242
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:24,680
Don't get the wrong idea.

243
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:27,120
My family is celebrating
the New Year here too.

244
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:29,095
I just wanted to wish your
mom a Happy New Year

245
00:18:29,119 --> 00:18:30,599
and talk to you about something else.

246
00:18:31,079 --> 00:18:31,880
What is it?

247
00:18:32,039 --> 00:18:34,359
Are you interested in working
for my family's company?

248
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:36,679
But I already have a job in Lan City.

249
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:37,680
I know.

250
00:18:38,039 --> 00:18:39,319
What I mean is,

251
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:41,199
if you're ever thinking of changing jobs,

252
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,599
you could consider our company.

253
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:44,839
I'll send you the job description.

254
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:46,278
The benefits are excellent.

255
00:18:46,279 --> 00:18:47,000
Zhuo Lan.

256
00:18:47,001 --> 00:18:48,279
I don't want to change jobs.

257
00:18:48,359 --> 00:18:49,240
And I probably

258
00:18:49,241 --> 00:18:50,279
never will.

259
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:53,960
Young lady.

260
00:18:54,079 --> 00:18:55,519
Here, have some fruit.

261
00:18:55,799 --> 00:18:56,839
Thank you, ma'am.

262
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:59,160
Why don't you stay for lunch?

263
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:02,519
Ma'am,
I can't stay for lunch.

264
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:05,000
I still have to visit some relatives.

265
00:19:06,079 --> 00:19:07,079
Yi-chen,

266
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:09,599
think about the job offer.

267
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:12,720
Ma'am, I'm leaving now.

268
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,359
Come visit again soon.

269
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:16,960
I will, ma'am.

270
00:19:19,839 --> 00:19:20,839
Yi-chen.

271
00:19:21,839 --> 00:19:22,880
Happy New Year.

272
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,240
Happy New Year.

273
00:19:25,799 --> 00:19:26,480
Goodbye, ma'am.

274
00:19:26,799 --> 00:19:27,799
Goodbye.

275
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:32,216
No wonder you didn't
want to go on a blind date.

276
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:33,759
So there's already someone.

277
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:35,720
Mom, she's not my girlfriend.

278
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:36,880
That girl's eyes

279
00:19:36,881 --> 00:19:38,359
were practically glued to you.

280
00:19:38,599 --> 00:19:40,319
And you're still trying to hide it from me?

281
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:42,039
She's really not my girlfriend.

282
00:19:42,839 --> 00:19:43,919
You mean you're not interested

283
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,080
in a wonderful girl like her?

284
00:19:45,359 --> 00:19:46,359
She's great,

285
00:19:46,559 --> 00:19:47,799
but she's not my type.

286
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,719
Then what is your type?

287
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:54,759
Tell me.

288
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:58,519
Mom, what's for breakfast?

289
00:20:00,759 --> 00:20:02,880
Mom, I'm hungry.

290
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:04,240
Mom.

291
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:06,640
What is it?

292
00:20:13,985 --> 00:20:15,591
[The only calls are for
Lu Feng and his brother]

293
00:20:16,215 --> 00:20:17,284
[Calling Lu Feng]

294
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:25,838
Mom, I'm so hungry.

295
00:20:25,839 --> 00:20:27,479
What are we eating?

296
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:28,519
Eat, eat, eat.

297
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:30,480
All you think about is food.

298
00:20:38,279 --> 00:20:39,798
Mom, Mom.

299
00:20:39,799 --> 00:20:40,799
We're leaving.

300
00:20:45,079 --> 00:20:45,599
How are you feeling?

301
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:46,680
Are you still feeling sick?

302
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:49,400
Maybe I shouldn't go either.

303
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:50,400
I can stay home and take care of you.
Don't worry about it.

304
00:20:51,519 --> 00:20:53,480
I'll take some medicine
and rest. I'll be fine.

305
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:56,039
You and Yi-chen should get going.

306
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:57,616
Otherwise, all the food auntie prepared

307
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:59,000
will go to waste.

308
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:01,319
Mom, he's is a grown man.

309
00:21:01,519 --> 00:21:02,639
He can take care of himself.

310
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:03,359
As for you,

311
00:21:03,360 --> 00:21:04,838
just relax and come with me and Qin Lang.

312
00:21:04,839 --> 00:21:05,640
That's all.

313
00:21:05,839 --> 00:21:06,839
Let's go.

314
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,039
Don't worry.

315
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:09,160
Let's go, let's go.

316
00:21:09,279 --> 00:21:10,640
Make sure you drink some water.

317
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:11,960
Let's go, Mom.

318
00:21:36,319 --> 00:21:37,319
Lu Feng.

319
00:21:39,559 --> 00:21:40,640
What are you doing here?

320
00:21:41,200 --> 00:21:43,120
I've been waiting
downstairs since this morning.

321
00:21:43,279 --> 00:21:44,279
Don't worry.

322
00:21:44,359 --> 00:21:45,679
I waited until I saw them leave

323
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:46,720
before I dared to come up.

324
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:03,680
Are you still eating?

325
00:22:11,240 --> 00:22:12,240
Lu Feng,

326
00:22:17,240 --> 00:22:19,119
do you remember the last class reunion?

327
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:20,960
I do.

328
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:23,839
I...

329
00:22:27,039 --> 00:22:28,599
Is it something bad?

330
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:32,279
If it's something bad, don't say it yet.

331
00:22:33,359 --> 00:22:35,240
The new year has just begun.

332
00:22:35,839 --> 00:22:37,759
Let's not say anything unhappy.

333
00:22:38,319 --> 00:22:39,838
That way, the rest of the year

334
00:22:39,839 --> 00:22:41,200
will go smoothly.

335
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:44,720
You never used to be this superstitious.

336
00:22:46,039 --> 00:22:47,799
That's because before,

337
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:51,519
I never had anyone I was afraid of losing.

338
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,680
I'm really worried

339
00:22:55,519 --> 00:22:56,960
you'll suddenly run away.

340
00:22:58,599 --> 00:22:59,839
I won't run away.

341
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:01,600
Even if you tried to chase me away,

342
00:23:01,759 --> 00:23:02,759
I might not leave.

343
00:23:03,839 --> 00:23:04,839
You said it.

344
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:25,680
What are you two doing?

345
00:23:26,240 --> 00:23:27,880
Mom, don't be angry.

346
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:29,799
It's my fault, Mom.

347
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:31,480
It's you.

348
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:34,079
Why are you here?

349
00:23:35,359 --> 00:23:37,278
Haven't you done enough to hurt my son?

350
00:23:37,279 --> 00:23:38,680
How dare you show your face?

351
00:23:41,839 --> 00:23:43,200
He's finally gotten better,

352
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,400
and you're here to bother him again.

353
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:47,440
Get out.

354
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:49,639
You're not welcome in our home.

355
00:23:49,640 --> 00:23:50,720
Get out!

356
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:51,960
Mom.

357
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:53,839
It's my fault. Please don't be angry.

358
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:55,640
Lu Feng, you should go.

359
00:23:56,359 --> 00:23:57,119
Lu Feng.

360
00:23:57,120 --> 00:23:58,200
Ma'am, please listen to me.

361
00:23:58,920 --> 00:24:00,200
My feelings for Xiao Chen

362
00:24:01,440 --> 00:24:02,440
are real.

363
00:24:07,079 --> 00:24:08,318
Lu Feng, just go.

364
00:24:08,319 --> 00:24:09,319
I'm begging you.

365
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:10,359
Lu Feng, hurry up and go.

366
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:11,518
Now is not the time to explain.

367
00:24:11,519 --> 00:24:13,000
If not now, then when?

368
00:24:14,359 --> 00:24:16,376
Are we supposed to hide
this for the rest of our lives?

369
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:18,838
Ma'am, he and Yi-chen are just colleagues.

370
00:24:18,839 --> 00:24:19,480
He heard Yi-chen was sick,
so he came to visit.

371
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:21,640
Lu Feng,
he has family to take care of him now.

372
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:23,640
You should go home.

373
00:24:24,599 --> 00:24:25,599
Colleagues?

374
00:24:27,359 --> 00:24:28,359
Then what about you two?

375
00:24:32,079 --> 00:24:34,200
You're dating Cheng
Yi-chen right now, aren't you?

376
00:24:35,039 --> 00:24:36,720
What gives you the right to be here?

377
00:24:37,119 --> 00:24:38,000
Mom.

378
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:39,400
Lu Feng is talking nonsense.
Don't believe him.

379
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:40,400
What?

380
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:42,359
'Right to be here'?

381
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:46,078
Mom, don't listen to Lu Feng.

382
00:24:46,079 --> 00:24:47,159
He's just making things up.

383
00:24:47,640 --> 00:24:48,640
Mom.

384
00:24:49,759 --> 00:24:50,440
Mom.

385
00:24:50,519 --> 00:24:53,079
Are you all trying to kill me?

386
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:54,880
Mom.

387
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:59,200
Mom.

388
00:25:00,119 --> 00:25:01,318
Mom.

389
00:25:01,319 --> 00:25:02,519
Ma'am, ma'am.

390
00:25:36,480 --> 00:25:37,759
Doctor, how is she?

391
00:25:38,119 --> 00:25:39,239
It's not looking good.

392
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:40,840
The family should prepare for the worst.

393
00:25:58,720 --> 00:26:00,480
Mom is this sick...

394
00:26:01,519 --> 00:26:03,119
and none of us even knew.

395
00:26:06,519 --> 00:26:07,519
Yi-chen.

396
00:26:08,599 --> 00:26:11,160
Go take care of the admission
paperwork. I'll go see Mom.

397
00:26:26,119 --> 00:26:27,119
Lu Feng.

398
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,319
Don't follow me.

399
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:33,680
I'm begging you.

400
00:26:36,279 --> 00:26:37,519
I won't go in with you.

401
00:26:39,079 --> 00:26:40,359
I'll just wait for you out here.

402
00:27:05,720 --> 00:27:06,440
Mom.

403
00:27:06,599 --> 00:27:08,039
Don't you call me Mom.

404
00:27:09,279 --> 00:27:11,559
You don't even see me as your mother.

405
00:27:12,319 --> 00:27:13,319
Mom...

406
00:27:14,599 --> 00:27:15,839
Don't bother crying.

407
00:27:17,640 --> 00:27:19,319
I don't have much time left.

408
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:21,359
When I'm dead,

409
00:27:21,360 --> 00:27:23,319
you can all do whatever you want.

410
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:26,519
It'll be as if I never had you two.

411
00:27:27,839 --> 00:27:29,359
All those years raising you...

412
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:31,000
were a complete waste.

413
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:34,680
Mom.

414
00:27:42,799 --> 00:27:43,799
Mom.

415
00:27:44,319 --> 00:27:45,079
Please, take your medicine.
I won't.

416
00:27:46,319 --> 00:27:48,160
It's just a waste of money.

417
00:27:48,279 --> 00:27:49,720
I'd be better off dead.

418
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,359
That's what you all want anyway.

419
00:27:54,119 --> 00:27:55,119
Mom.

420
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,440
Don't say that.

421
00:27:59,319 --> 00:28:00,720
Am I wrong?

422
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:03,999
You're all grown up and successful now.

423
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:05,759
You don't have to listen to me anymore.

424
00:28:06,559 --> 00:28:08,318
I'd rather join your father sooner

425
00:28:08,319 --> 00:28:12,680
than watch you carry on
with this shameful business.

426
00:28:15,839 --> 00:28:16,839
Mom.

427
00:28:18,519 --> 00:28:20,759
Lu Feng and I are truly in love.

428
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:23,039
It's just that we...

429
00:28:24,279 --> 00:28:25,439
Yi-chen, he...

430
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:26,759
Shut up.

431
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:28,518
Don't you mention Yi-chen.

432
00:28:28,519 --> 00:28:32,160
You're the one who corrupted him.

433
00:29:08,920 --> 00:29:11,799
I couldn't even bear to spend this money.

434
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,999
I saved up all of this.

435
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:17,000
Look.

436
00:29:19,200 --> 00:29:21,358
I never touched a single cent of it.

437
00:29:21,359 --> 00:29:24,720
I was saving it all for
you to start a family.

438
00:29:26,559 --> 00:29:27,559
Xiao Chen.

439
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:30,278
I raised two sons.

440
00:29:30,279 --> 00:29:32,799
At least one of them has to be normal.

441
00:29:34,519 --> 00:29:37,399
Xiao Chen, you're the older brother.

442
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:39,440
You're more sensible than Yi-chen.

443
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:43,680
I'm begging you.

444
00:29:59,680 --> 00:30:01,079
I suddenly realized

445
00:30:01,279 --> 00:30:02,839
that my mother has grown old.

446
00:30:03,519 --> 00:30:04,999
I have never been so afraid

447
00:30:05,000 --> 00:30:06,000
that Mom

448
00:30:06,039 --> 00:30:07,920
might leave us one day.

449
00:30:27,680 --> 00:30:29,039
Your eyes are so swollen.

450
00:30:55,359 --> 00:30:56,359
Do you have a cigarette?

451
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,400
Slow down.

452
00:31:24,119 --> 00:31:25,119
Lu Feng.

453
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:27,000
My mom has a heart condition.

454
00:31:27,759 --> 00:31:29,079
It's very serious.

455
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:35,160
Between Yi-chen and me,

456
00:31:36,559 --> 00:31:37,839
one of us has to

457
00:31:38,519 --> 00:31:39,519
do our duty as sons.

458
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,359
Yi-chen is still young.

459
00:31:49,319 --> 00:31:50,400
What are you getting at?

460
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:54,200
Maybe...

461
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:56,720
we should just...

462
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:58,759
stop seeing each other for a while.

463
00:32:04,599 --> 00:32:06,119
Is that a suggestion,

464
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:09,839
or is this your final decision?

465
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:11,440
With things the way they are,

466
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:13,960
I have to answer to my mom.

467
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:30,000
So what am I to you?

468
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:40,160
Fine.

469
00:32:40,759 --> 00:32:42,240
We can take a break.

470
00:32:43,519 --> 00:32:44,519
And then what?

471
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,720
Your brother is still young.

472
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,480
You have to be his good older brother.

473
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:52,920
Listen to your mother.

474
00:32:53,160 --> 00:32:54,119
Get married, have kids.
Carry on the family line.

475
00:32:54,721 --> 00:32:55,920
Be the perfect, dutiful son.

476
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:58,240
And what about me?

477
00:33:02,759 --> 00:33:03,759
Xiao Chen.

478
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:07,559
How can you be so
considerate of everyone else,

479
00:33:07,599 --> 00:33:09,119
and just leave me out?

480
00:33:10,519 --> 00:33:11,440
Do you think that by doing this,
you're being noble?

481
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,160
First your mother,

482
00:33:14,279 --> 00:33:15,359
then your brother,

483
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:16,880
you even consider Qin Lang.

484
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:18,880
And I'm dead last.

485
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:22,200
In your eyes, is our relationship

486
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:24,880
really

487
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:26,839
not worth fighting for?

488
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:29,160
Lu Feng.

489
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:32,519
My mom's condition is really serious.

490
00:33:33,759 --> 00:33:35,200
Your mom, your mom...

491
00:33:35,279 --> 00:33:36,640
It's always your mom.

492
00:33:37,480 --> 00:33:38,480
What about me?

493
00:33:39,079 --> 00:33:41,559
Do you think it was nothing
for me to cut ties with my family?

494
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:44,320
That it was just something
I was supposed to do?

495
00:33:44,359 --> 00:33:46,599
Do you think you're the
only one making sacrifices?

496
00:33:48,279 --> 00:33:49,559
I turned my back on everyone.

497
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:51,440
My dad.

498
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,480
My sister.

499
00:33:52,839 --> 00:33:54,318
All to be with you.

500
00:33:54,319 --> 00:33:55,720
And you? Cheng Yichen.

501
00:33:58,559 --> 00:33:59,759
You'd rather betray me.

502
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:06,920
I get it now.

503
00:34:09,079 --> 00:34:10,559
You telling me all this,

504
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:13,079
it's all just an excuse.

505
00:34:17,480 --> 00:34:19,920
Is it because you've
already found someone else?

506
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:25,400
That's right.

507
00:34:25,719 --> 00:34:26,879
You hit the nail on the head.

508
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:28,760
I haven't liked you for a long time.

509
00:34:29,079 --> 00:34:30,639
I've never even looked up to you.

510
00:34:31,559 --> 00:34:32,400
Since being with me

511
00:34:32,401 --> 00:34:33,559
has cost you so much,

512
00:34:34,639 --> 00:34:37,599
why don't we skip the 'break'?

513
00:34:38,519 --> 00:34:39,840
Let's just break up for good.

514
00:34:43,719 --> 00:34:45,319
Then you won't have to give anything up.

515
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:48,000
You can go back to your life of luxury.

516
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:52,440
Cheng Yichen.

517
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,519
Have I been too easy on you?

518
00:34:56,599 --> 00:34:57,695
Has it made you this arrogant?

519
00:34:57,719 --> 00:34:59,359
Say 'break up' one more time. I dare you.

520
00:35:00,159 --> 00:35:02,000
Fine, let's break up.

521
00:35:05,519 --> 00:35:07,159
We should have broken up a long time ago.

522
00:35:07,559 --> 00:35:09,695
Someone like you who'll do
anything to get what they want...

523
00:35:09,719 --> 00:35:11,599
who's to say you wouldn't
just dump me one day?

524
00:35:12,239 --> 00:35:13,239
In that case,

525
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:14,519
we might as well break up.

526
00:35:17,719 --> 00:35:18,719
Break up.

527
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:19,960
Let's go.

528
00:35:21,639 --> 00:35:23,199
Lu Feng, what are you doing?

529
00:35:28,480 --> 00:35:30,159
Lu Feng, what are you doing?

530
00:35:30,239 --> 00:35:31,599
You want to break up, right?

531
00:35:31,840 --> 00:35:33,480
Cheng Yichen, let me tell you something.

532
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:36,160
You're too scared to face your mom.

533
00:35:36,320 --> 00:35:37,600
Too scared to face your brother.

534
00:35:38,199 --> 00:35:39,199
So I'll do it.

535
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,159
I'll go talk to them.
Lu Feng.

536
00:35:40,639 --> 00:35:41,480
Don't threaten him.

537
00:35:41,481 --> 00:35:43,121
What are you going to talk to them about?

538
00:35:43,159 --> 00:35:45,360
You'll only make things worse.

539
00:35:51,719 --> 00:35:54,079
If you want your mom to be okay,

540
00:35:54,159 --> 00:35:55,159
then you'll shut up.

541
00:36:00,679 --> 00:36:02,519
And you'll wait here
quietly until I get back.

542
00:36:05,159 --> 00:36:06,718
They say a love like ours,

543
00:36:06,719 --> 00:36:08,239
no matter how unconventional,

544
00:36:08,880 --> 00:36:10,199
doesn't hurt anyone else.

545
00:36:11,679 --> 00:36:14,519
But we clearly have.

546
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:16,360
My heart is beating so fast.

547
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:18,320
I don't know why.

548
00:36:18,321 --> 00:36:19,800
It's like I can sense it.

549
00:36:20,559 --> 00:36:22,639
Something ominous is approaching.

550
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:25,360
I'm about to lose him.

551
00:36:26,559 --> 00:36:28,039
About to lose something.

552
00:36:30,639 --> 00:36:31,959
Are you two breaking up too?

553
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:33,360
What's gotten into you now?

554
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:35,238
Your mom wants us to break up.

555
00:36:35,239 --> 00:36:36,559
Your brother has already agreed.

556
00:36:37,079 --> 00:36:38,119
So I'm asking you.

557
00:36:38,519 --> 00:36:39,519
You.

558
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:40,840
And him.

559
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:42,079
Are you breaking up?

560
00:36:43,639 --> 00:36:45,000
If you two don't want to break up,

561
00:36:45,079 --> 00:36:46,839
then come with me to
see your mom right now.

562
00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:48,920
Make her accept us.

563
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:50,840
Let's all just calm down.

564
00:36:51,519 --> 00:36:52,519
Right now, the priority

565
00:36:52,880 --> 00:36:54,559
is their mother's health.

566
00:36:55,519 --> 00:36:56,519
No.

567
00:36:56,679 --> 00:36:57,840
There's no time left.

568
00:36:58,800 --> 00:36:59,919
Who did you say has no time left?

569
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:01,038
Who has no time left?

570
00:37:01,039 --> 00:37:02,518
What are you freaking out about?

571
00:37:02,519 --> 00:37:03,839
I wasn't talking about your mom.

572
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:05,159
How dare you mention my mother?

573
00:37:05,199 --> 00:37:06,199
If it weren't for you,

574
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:07,600
my mom wouldn't have collapsed.

575
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:09,279
I told you to leave. Why didn't you?

576
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,400
Why didn't you get out?

577
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:12,976
Bad things always happen to
my brother when you're around.

578
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:14,400
Why do you have to ruin my brother?

579
00:37:14,519 --> 00:37:15,400
Why do you have to ruin us?
Why?

580
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:21,920
Yi-chen.

581
00:37:22,239 --> 00:37:23,239
Yi-chen.

582
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:39,480
Does it hurt?

583
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:41,679
Lu Feng, where did you go?

584
00:37:41,760 --> 00:37:42,760
What took you so long?

585
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:43,760
Did you go see my mom?

586
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:44,840
Don't worry.

587
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:46,000
I didn't go see her.

588
00:37:47,559 --> 00:37:48,760
The holiday is almost over.

589
00:37:49,753 --> 00:37:51,032
Once we get back to Lan City...

590
00:37:51,119 --> 00:37:52,559
your mom can't do anything to us.

591
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:53,880
Come on, let's go.

592
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,039
Qin Lang, what are you doing?

593
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:58,518
What am I doing?

594
00:37:58,519 --> 00:38:00,239
Ask him! Go on, ask him!

595
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:02,198
Don't you know Yi-chen's leg is broken?

596
00:38:02,199 --> 00:38:03,360
Do you have any idea?

597
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:08,280
Lu Feng.

598
00:38:10,119 --> 00:38:11,320
What happened?

599
00:38:14,519 --> 00:38:16,599
He fell pretty hard.

600
00:38:17,239 --> 00:38:19,880
The coccyx and sacrum
are in a very delicate position.

601
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:22,519
His neurological functions
have been severely affected.

602
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,039
I suggest you...

603
00:38:24,040 --> 00:38:26,055
transfer him to a larger,
better-equipped hospital immediately...

604
00:38:26,079 --> 00:38:28,119
and get him a high-resolution MRI.

605
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,880
Doctor...

606
00:38:31,559 --> 00:38:34,440
is there a chance he'll be paralyzed?

607
00:38:35,199 --> 00:38:36,119
It's hard to say.

608
00:38:36,120 --> 00:38:38,760
We'll know more after
we see the MRI results.

609
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:42,440
Okay, Doctor.

610
00:38:42,519 --> 00:38:43,919
I'll go take care of it right away.

611
00:38:49,719 --> 00:38:50,719
Thank you, Doctor.

612
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,000
How's your brother?

613
00:39:00,159 --> 00:39:01,440
Get the hell away from me.

614
00:39:04,639 --> 00:39:05,639
Xiao Chen.

615
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:07,079
I really didn't mean to.

616
00:39:08,440 --> 00:39:09,320
I never thought...

617
00:39:09,321 --> 00:39:10,721
things would turn out like this.

618
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:11,840
Please, believe me.

619
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:15,000
Just go.

620
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:18,760
Don't come looking for me again.
